reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to use, cleans up really easy
reviews.reviewText: This fryer basket actually does what they claim. I use it to do zucchini chips, potato type chips, even have done Roma Tomato crips. So far I'm pleased with what I have expected and put upon it. My next expectation is clean up, it so far has done well. I have NOT put in dishwasher to see what happens. But happy with what I do at the moment.
